{"tid":1864951,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"何雁詩1萬港元掃10幾個口罩：肉痛好過喉嚨痛","createTime":"2020-02-06T02:05:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T03:37:31.000Z","uid":213877,"like":2,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"74d93a90052b7f3e2860ca38390797c059f1a7dd","tid":1864951,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T02:05:48.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情持續蔓延，全城陷口罩荒，現時一罩難求，就算成功撲到口罩，都要留意戴罩方法，亦要留意是否買了二手口罩，或有沒有被抬高價。何雁詩昨晚在instagram的限時動態留言，自爆以1萬元買了10幾個可重用及換filter的口罩，平均1個口罩要近千元，十分誇張，她說：「just spent almost $10k on masks﹗為咗希望個個人都可以買到，我只係幫咗有需要的親戚朋友買咗每人一個，加埋一包filter，總共買咗10幾個可重用/換filter的口罩，都要1萬$啦，desperate times desperate measures&hellip;肉痛仲（總）好過喉嚨痛。」<img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0hWF-gnCiOCGkQHiA65t53PilICwYjchtqdChZdk9wVl1pLEpof3BBBzNMU1o5J083fi9FCjBbVwo7Lkw8JX4/w644\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fobs.line-scdn.net%2F0hWF-gnCiOCGkQHiA65t53PilICwYjchtqdChZdk9wVl1pLEpof3BBBzNMU1o5J083fi9FCjBbVwo7Lkw8JX4%2Fw644&h=3b4eff7b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0hITgUJ_2yFntaLD4orOxpLGN6FRRpQAV4PhpHZAVCSE8jHlR6NUJfFXl8Sxt3T1ElNB1bGHdpSRhxHFIub0w/w644\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fobs.line-scdn.net%2F0hITgUJ_2yFntaLD4orOxpLGN6FRRpQAV4PhpHZAVCSE8jHlR6NUJfFXl8Sxt3T1ElNB1bGHdpSRhxHFIub0w%2Fw644&h=676123a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://today.line.me/hk/pc/article/【好誇張】何雁詩1萬港元掃10幾個口罩：肉痛好過喉嚨痛-YXR66W\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftoday.line.me%2Fhk%2Fpc%2Farticle%2F%E3%80%90%E5%A5%BD%E8%AA%87%E5%BC%B5%E3%80%91%E4%BD%95%E9%9B%81%E8%A9%A91%E8%90%AC%E6%B8%AF%E5%85%83%E6%8E%8310%E5%B9%BE%E5%80%8B%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%EF%BC%9A%E8%82%89%E7%97%9B%E5%A5%BD%E9%81%8E%E5%96%89%E5%9A%A8%E7%97%9B-YXR66W&d=SLV77eIUGxkMmCzjf2iSt8VJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=efe0e84d\" target=\"_blank\">https://today.line.me/hk/pc/article/【好誇張】何雁詩1萬港元掃10幾個口罩：肉痛好過喉嚨痛-YXR66W</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n有錢人果然係唔同D</sp